translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_67a83756:

    # pc "Okay, I'm going inside."
    pc "好的，我进去了。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:223
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_aebc2109:

    # "I make my way in, shining the flashlight all around, my heart pounding."
    "我小心翼翼地走进去，手电筒四处照着，心跳如鼓。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:224
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_e77bbc81:

    # "Every second, I expect to hear sirens, or to hear somebody yell at me or to see somebody pop out from behind a corner."
    "每一秒，我都以为会听到警笛声，或者有人朝我大喊，又或者有人从拐角处窜出来。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:225
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_28a77d2c:

    # "Every part of me knows this is wrong."
    "我全身的每个细胞都在告诉我，这不对劲。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:228
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_e5081e4c:

    # "When I get to the office, I turn on the lamp and take a look around."
    "到了办公室，我打开台灯环顾四周。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:229
