# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:235
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_443a82ad:

    # pc "I see it."
    pc "我看到了。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:236
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_4c06e02c:

    # wt "Good. Let me know when you're ready and I'll read you the code again."
    wt "好。准备好了就告诉我，我再念一遍密码给你听。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:239
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_c7de4069:

    # pc "Ready."
    pc "准备好了。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:240
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_e95b465f:

    # wt "The code is 96678552."
    wt "密码是96678552。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:241
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_e5efc8d0:

    # "I poke the code in, careful to get every number correct, and when I press the final number, there is an audible click that makes me jump back a bit and the safe door opens up slightly."
    "我小心翼翼地输入密码，确保每个数字都准确无误。当我按下最后一个数字时，传来一声清脆的咔嗒声，吓得我往后退了一步，保险柜门微微打开。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:244
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_01540178:

    # pc "It's open. There's a bunch of boxes in here. You said they're at the bottom?"
    pc "打开了。里面有一堆盒子。你说它们在最下面？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:245
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_0a9be0ab:

    # wt "Yes, it was on the lowest shelf. I think the box second from the right. They might all have gems in them though."
    wt "是的，就在最底层的架子上。我记得是右起第二个盒子。不过里面可能全都是宝石。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:246
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_9ba477c1:

    # pc "Okay, I'm looking for it."
    pc "好的，我正在找。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:249
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_10d5b864:

    # pc "I think I found it. Box full of baggies."
    pc "我好像找到了。箱子里全是小袋子。"

