    # "I dig through the box while Whitney drives frantically, taking the turns way too fast, my pulse still racing."
    "惠特尼疯狂地开车，过弯时速度快得离谱，我的心跳依然狂飙，我一边翻找着箱子。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:290
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_212a14ef:

    # pc "I found a 4.2 and a 4.07."
    pc "我找到了一颗4.2克拉和一颗4.07克拉的。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:291
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_6bac06fc:

    # wt "Perfect! YES!"
    wt "太棒了！太好了！"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:292
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_5e27f974:

    # pc "I think I'm going to throw up."
    pc "我觉得我要吐了。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:293
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_92aba439:

    # wt "Wait till we get back to my house. We're almost in the clear."
    wt "等回到我家再说。我们快安全了。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:296
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_96281544:

    # wt "You did it!"
    wt "你做到了！"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:297
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_016dba66:

    # pc "Yes, I did. I am now a diamond thief."
    pc "是的，我做到了。我现在是个钻石大盗。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:298
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_a4f3809c:

    # pc "What are we going to do with all those extra diamonds?"
    pc "这些多出来的钻石我们该怎么办？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:299
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_557a741e:

    # wt "I don't know. Fund other projects? Who knows, we may need them to get your father back. They will have a use."
    wt "我不知道。用来资助其他项目？谁知道呢，说不定我们需要它们来救回你父亲。总会有用处的。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:300
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_09a265e5:

    # wt "And that shop is insured. They won't lose anything."
    wt "而且那家店有保险。他们不会损失分文。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:301
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_23b2d4a7:

    # wt "Whatever we use them for it will be for a greater purpose than jewelry."
    wt "无论我们把它们用在什么地方，都比当首饰更有意义。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:304
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_d8c025fe:

    # pc "I'm sorry, but this is all so much. I feel really conflicted about it."
    pc "对不起，但这实在太过分了。我对此感到非常矛盾。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:305
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_0228ab4a:

    # pc "You don't feel bad that we just broke the law and stole several thousand dollars worth of diamonds?"
    pc "你不觉得我们刚刚违法偷了价值几千美元的钻石很过分吗？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:306
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_74d8401f:

    # wt "It's more like several hundred thousand dollars worth."
    wt "其实价值好几百万美元呢。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:307
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_3b11b6ba:

    # pc "What the fuck, really!?"
    pc "这他妈的，真的！？"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:308
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_210e65ff:

    # wt "Yes, the four carat diamonds alone are valued at over $100,000 each."
    wt "是的，光是那四颗四克拉的钻石，每颗价值就超过10万美元。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:309
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_b74f3f5d:

    # pc "I'm going to be sick."
    pc "我快吐了。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:312
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_bba46494:

    # wt "To answer your question, no, I do not feel bad about it."
    wt "回答你的问题，不，我对此毫无愧疚。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:313
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_44524cb3:

    # wt "We did not hurt anybody. What we are doing will help people."
    wt "我们没伤害任何人。我们所做的事会帮助到别人。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:314
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_aa32b9ba:

    # wt "Sometimes, to great minds, the law does not apply. All that matters is the outcome."
    wt "有时候，对伟大的头脑来说，法律并不适用。唯一重要的是结果。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:318
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_8a64798d:

    # wt "I don't know about you, but that got my heart pumping really good."
    wt "不知道你怎么看，但这让我心跳加速。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:319
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_ea619a7a:

    # wt "I feel very stimulated right now."
    wt "我现在感觉特别兴奋。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:320
translate chinese rjwhitneywarning_d4a5ac2e:

    # wt "Can we go to my bedroom? I want to have sex with you very badly."
    wt "我们去我卧室好吗？我特别想和你做爱。"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:324
